OL,3,CMan who fell victim to paternity fraud
OL,4,Csays his 'life was ruined'
OL,6,FA man from Cheshire whose ex-partner
OL,7,Flied to him about being the father of
OL,8,Fher child says his "life has been
OL,9,Fruined".
OL,11,FRyan Hampson fell victim to paternity
OL,12,Ffraud when his former girlfriend
OL,13,Fscammed him into believing he was the
OL,14,Ffather of her baby.
OL,16,FBeth Fernley, 26, told Ryan Hampson
OL,17,Fshe was pregnant and was unsure about
OL,18,Fwho the baby's father was, in April
OL,19,F2019.
