OL,3,CMan who fell victim to paternity fraud
OL,4,Csays his 'life was ruined'
OL,6,FRyan said he spent 18 months with the
OL,7,Fbaby, who he formed a "strong bond"
OL,8,Fwith.
OL,10,FHe said: "I can't put into words how I
OL,11,Ffelt...I was in a very dark place for
OL,12,Fa very long time."
OL,14,FRyan's mum Claire Hampson told Good
OL,15,FMorning Britain: "We adored the
OL,16,Fbaby...we bonded and invested
OL,17,Feverything we had."
OL,19,FClaire said when Ryan showed her the
OL,20,Fforged letter, she knew straight away
OL,21,Fit was fake.
