OL,3,CMan who fell victim to paternity fraud
OL,4,Csays his 'life was ruined'
OL,6,FClaire said: "I was so torn.
OL,8,F"I was trying to come to terms with
OL,9,Fthe fact that my granddaughter wasn't
OL,10,Fmy granddaughter, and at the same time
OL,11,FI watched my son's life fall apart."
OL,13,FRyan told the programme he is
OL,14,Freceiving counselling and trying to
OL,15,Frebuild his life.
OL,17,FThe trial at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,18,Fheard Ryan Hampson was at the baby's
OL,19,Fbirth, named on the birth certificate
OL,20,Fand bought a house with Beth Fernley
OL,21,Fin 2020.
